[Warm on a Cold Night]

3
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:38,039
[Episode 17]

4
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,210
Painter Feng is so diligent.

5
00:01:42,390 --> 00:01:43,740
He never stops practicing.

6
00:01:43,740 --> 00:01:45,420
But for two years,

7
00:01:45,570 --> 00:01:47,170
he didn't produce anything.

8
00:01:47,289 --> 00:01:48,220
That was the time

9
00:01:48,620 --> 00:01:49,880
he studied abroad.

10
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:55,220
We missed

11
00:01:55,220 --> 00:01:56,420
such an obvious clue.

12
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:57,800
Meng Huaiyun died

13
00:01:58,330 --> 00:02:00,270
and the painting immortal appeared

14
00:02:00,270 --> 00:02:02,580
on New Year's Eve of the 29th year of the Dingkun reign.

15
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:03,330
That means

16
00:02:03,830 --> 00:02:04,690
he was actually

17
00:02:05,110 --> 00:02:07,040
studying in the far east back then.

18
00:02:08,509 --> 00:02:09,600
I see.

19
00:02:16,860 --> 00:02:17,700
He escaped.

20
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:20,780
That table

21
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:22,610
was moved.

22
00:02:47,650 --> 00:02:49,310
There's a secret tunnel here.

23
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:55,700
Hurry up.

24
00:02:57,460 --> 00:02:57,940
Come on.

25
00:03:02,250 --> 00:03:02,910
Be careful.

26
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:04,350
Be careful.

27
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:20,740
My master has arthritis in his legs.

28
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:22,350
For a while, he couldn't walk,

29
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:23,380
so there is a chair like this

30
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:24,450
in the studio.

31
00:03:26,660 --> 00:03:27,590
The lamp is here.

32
00:03:50,110 --> 00:03:51,710
Isn't this Master Wei 's fan?

33
00:03:54,650 --> 00:03:56,250
So Wei Gonglin hasn't been traveling.

34
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:57,660
He has been imprisoned here.

35
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:58,620
His money was taken

36
00:03:58,620 --> 00:04:00,140
to redeem Meng Huaiyun's paintings.

37
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:01,200
Look at the ground.

38
00:04:01,510 --> 00:04:03,140
Those are wheelchair tracks.

39
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:04,240
That means

40
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:05,230
Feng Muyuan

41
00:04:05,260 --> 00:04:06,300
has been lying to us all along.

42
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:07,020
Wei Gonglin's leg

43
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:08,080
hasn't recovered.

44
00:04:10,060 --> 00:04:11,060
That's not right.

45
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:12,710
Then who was the person

46
00:04:12,970 --> 00:04:13,970
who attacked him?

47
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:16,079
And why hasn't he killed

48
00:04:16,110 --> 00:04:17,130
Wei Gonglin?

49
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,220
Isn't it more difficult

50
00:04:19,300 --> 00:04:20,899
to imprison a living person?

51
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:21,870
Could it be...

52
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:23,940
the masked man is his accomplice

53
00:04:23,940 --> 00:04:25,880
and has been helping him in secret the whole time?

54
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,340
The gas lamp just went out.

55
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:29,240
He can't have gone far.

56
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,850
I don't care.

57
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:33,930
Don't try to get rid of me this time.

58
00:04:33,930 --> 00:04:34,670
We agreed

59
00:04:34,700 --> 00:04:36,220
we would catch him together.

60
00:04:36,220 --> 00:04:37,520
I won't be a burden.

61
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,030
Get off.

62
00:04:39,100 --> 00:04:39,450
No.

63
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,420
Hold on tight.

64
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:47,159
A partner like me

65
00:04:47,550 --> 00:04:48,550
is hard to come by.

66
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,290
Your Highness.

67
00:04:50,820 --> 00:04:51,860
Go and get

68
00:04:51,890 --> 00:04:53,360
everyone from the Inspection Bureau.

69
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:53,909
Let's go.

70
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,220
Where do I find you?

71
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:06,930
My disciple,

72
00:05:07,890 --> 00:05:09,610
I was wrong.

73
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:11,630
I had always thought

74
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,360
you were the most foolish amongst your peers,

75
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,090
and had no talent for painting,

76
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:18,400
so I hadn't taken good care of you.

77
00:05:18,740 --> 00:05:20,830
But since you've came back from the far east,

78
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:22,410
you have impressed me.

79
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,920
Although you've been hiding your true skill in painting,

80
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,170
I can see that

81
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,230
after you achieve a breakthrough,

82
00:05:28,230 --> 00:05:29,230
it won't take long

83
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:31,040
before you surpass me.

84
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:32,680
My disciple,

85
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,020
why are you so persistent

86
00:05:35,020 --> 00:05:36,900
about heartlessly destroying everything?

87
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:38,380
Let it go.

88
00:05:40,140 --> 00:05:41,100
Where is

89
00:05:42,340 --> 00:05:43,480
Huaiyun’s body?

90
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:44,700
It's not worth it

91
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,760
to ruin your own future

92
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,720
even if it's for Huaiyun's sake.

93
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:50,120
I loved Huaiyun so much.

94
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:52,480
But if I didn't keep the secret for them,

95
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,880
Nanfeng Studio would have been destroyed.

96
00:05:54,990 --> 00:05:55,580
Do you really think

97
00:05:55,580 --> 00:05:57,630
if you conceal the whereabouts of her body,

98
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,200
and the evidence doesn't surface,

99
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:01,180
that you would be able to live your life anew?

100
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:01,640
Master.

101
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,400
The world already knows

102
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,400
your true colors.

103
00:06:04,530 --> 00:06:05,950
I didn't kill Huaiyun.

104
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:08,000
I just made a choice.

105
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,530
I waited until today

106
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,690
to make you see

107
00:06:13,060 --> 00:06:14,780
it is your so-called choice

108
00:06:15,370 --> 00:06:16,900
that ruins Nanfeng Studio!

109
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:31,930
Tell me.

110
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,200
Where did you hide her?

111
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:09,110
My disciple,

112
00:07:09,260 --> 00:07:11,070
I've told you everything.

113
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:12,400
For old time's sake,

114
00:07:12,550 --> 00:07:13,750
please spare my life.

115
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:14,990
I never knew

116
00:07:15,020 --> 00:07:16,920
you and Yun had a relationship like this.

117
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,770
You've always done everything

118
00:07:17,770 --> 00:07:18,720
in silence.

119
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,410
Why do this to yourself?

120
00:07:20,430 --> 00:07:21,300
If you leave this sentiment

121
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:21,820
in painting—

122
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:22,580
Shut up!

123
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:35,790
Don't come here!

124
00:07:36,340 --> 00:07:37,020
Stay away!

125
00:07:37,580 --> 00:07:38,170
Otherwise,

126
00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:39,570
I'll kill him right this moment!

127
00:07:39,570 --> 00:07:40,070
Calm down,

128
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:40,870
Painter Feng.

129
00:07:41,810 --> 00:07:42,730
Calm down.

130
00:07:44,260 --> 00:07:45,470
I'll calm him down first.

131
00:07:45,470 --> 00:07:47,200
You take the chance to save him.

132
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:48,460
Don't be impulsive.

133
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,860
I'm not good at swimming.

134
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:52,720
I'm afraid I won't be able to take care of you.

135
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:58,220
Painter Feng.

136
00:07:59,230 --> 00:08:01,500
Are you waiting for someone?

137
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,200
Who?

138
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,730
That man yesterday

139
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:06,900
was your accomplice,

140
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:07,360
right?

141
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,880
If I say I have no accomplice,

142
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,120
would you believe me?

143
00:08:12,450 --> 00:08:13,650
How is that possible?

144
00:08:14,660 --> 00:08:15,460
In this world,

145
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:17,490
I don't have partners

146
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:18,990
nor a family.

147
00:08:19,770 --> 00:08:20,900
Even if someone like me

148
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:21,830
disappeared,

149
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:23,920
no one will notice.

150
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:26,020
Just like Junior.

151
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,200
Painter Feng.

152
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,700
Why are you doing this?

153
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:31,160
She will never know

154
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:33,220
about your avenging her,

155
00:08:34,010 --> 00:08:35,210
nor your love for her.

156
00:08:36,260 --> 00:08:36,760
Right?

157
00:08:39,710 --> 00:08:40,460
So what?

158
00:08:42,539 --> 00:08:43,880
I don't deserve her.

159
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:46,620
It's all because of me...

160
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:48,690
I didn't protect her.

161
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:51,500
Back then,

162
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:54,520
I was only a junior disciple in Nanfeng Studio.

163
00:08:54,520 --> 00:08:55,400
All I did were menial tasks

164
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,930
like serving tea and water.

165
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:59,000
I learned painting in secret,

166
00:08:59,140 --> 00:09:01,600
hoping Master would take me as his disciple.

167
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:03,800
Senior, please have some tea.

168
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:08,860
And she

169
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,100
was just an apprentice who came to learn painting

170
00:09:11,100 --> 00:09:12,050
once in a while.

171
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:14,540
She hadn't become a disciple yet.

172
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:15,610
Go.

173
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:17,590
Serve that lady tea.

174
00:09:18,140 --> 00:09:19,300
What kind of beautiful painting

175
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,160
could such an ugly person create?

176
00:09:22,250 --> 00:09:22,890
Go.

177
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:24,730
Go.

178
00:09:38,260 --> 00:09:38,720
Senior.

179
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:40,230
I'm too clumsy.

180
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:42,420
I'll make some tea for you again.

181
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,780
Three years later,

182
00:09:46,890 --> 00:09:47,750
Master finally accepted

183
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:49,210
his only female disciple.

184
00:09:50,430 --> 00:09:51,530
From a distance,

185
00:09:52,420 --> 00:09:53,300
I thought her eyes

186
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:54,560
looked very familiar.

187
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:57,740
She was extraordinarily gifted.

188
00:09:57,740 --> 00:09:58,690
The entire Nanfeng Studio

189
00:09:58,690 --> 00:10:00,080
treated her like a star,

190
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:03,280
but she kept her distance from everyone.

191
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:03,770
Junior.

192
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:04,560
Don’t go.

193
00:10:04,580 --> 00:10:05,820
Where are you going?
Don’t go.

194
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:06,560
At that time,

195
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,960
although I was no longer a junior disciple,

196
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,030
I still had to do menial tasks

197
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:11,070
for my seniors.

198
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:29,040
Junior.

199
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,020
Senior.

200
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,850
Why are you still so stupid?

201
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,000
Still?

202
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,350
We seldom talked,

203
00:10:53,090 --> 00:10:54,300
but we always hid out

204
00:10:54,330 --> 00:10:55,860
in the warehouse together.

205
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:57,270
We just wanted

206
00:10:57,300 --> 00:10:58,560
a quiet place to paint.

207
00:11:00,250 --> 00:11:01,980
Although she didn't talk much,

208
00:11:01,980 --> 00:11:02,650
I knew

209
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:05,030
it wasn't because she was aloof,

210
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:07,990
but because her background was complicated.

211
00:11:09,100 --> 00:11:10,980
When she first came to Nanfeng Studio,

212
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:11,990
I've already heard that

213
00:11:11,990 --> 00:11:12,700
the youngest daughter

214
00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,920
of an official from Jiuxiao City

215
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:15,450
had a birthmark on her face.

216
00:11:15,930 --> 00:11:16,890
A few years later,

217
00:11:16,890 --> 00:11:18,510
when Master brought her back,

218
00:11:18,510 --> 00:11:19,220
I heard that

219
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:21,320
the official's property had been confiscated

220
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:23,180
and his family had been beheaded.

221
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:25,460
Only the youngest daughter with a birthmark on her face

222
00:11:25,460 --> 00:11:26,460
had gone missing.

223
00:11:32,130 --> 00:11:33,190
Junior's painting

224
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:35,070
was taken by the palace again.

225
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:36,200
I've also heard that

226
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:37,520
the Empress Dowager wants Junior

227
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:39,300
to paint another one on her birthday.

228
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:40,950
Junior was getting better and better at painting,

229
00:11:40,950 --> 00:11:42,080
and her name spread.

230
00:11:42,230 --> 00:11:43,300
Her painting was sent to the palace

231
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:44,850
and recongized by the Empress Dowager.

232
00:11:44,850 --> 00:11:45,380
As for me,

233
00:11:45,660 --> 00:11:46,900
I was still

234
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,730
a nobody in Nanfeng Studio.

235
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:50,380
Muyuan.

236
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:51,620
Monk Suoluo

237
00:11:51,780 --> 00:11:53,140
likes your painting.

238
00:11:53,770 --> 00:11:55,380
He thinks you should meet each other.

239
00:11:55,380 --> 00:11:57,870
He invites you to go to the far east with him

240
00:11:58,220 --> 00:11:59,780
to hone your painting skills.

241
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:00,310
Master,

242
00:12:00,640 --> 00:12:00,920
I...

243
00:12:01,210 --> 00:12:01,940
My disciple.

244
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:03,930
This is a great opportunity.

245
00:12:04,330 --> 00:12:05,330
But you can decide

246
00:12:06,300 --> 00:12:07,900
whether you want to go or not.

247
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:25,980
Thank you, Master.

248
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:28,940
Congratulations, Senior.

249
00:12:28,940 --> 00:12:29,650
Congratulations.

250
00:12:29,650 --> 00:12:30,430
Congratulations.

251
00:12:30,430 --> 00:12:31,170
Congratulations.

252
00:12:31,170 --> 00:12:31,760
Congratulations.

253
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:32,690
Congratulations.

254
00:12:32,690 --> 00:12:34,220
I didn't think that would be

255
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:36,150
the last time we saw each other.

256
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,570
Two years later,

257
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:41,510
I came back to Nanfeng Studio and learned that

258
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:44,180
Junior had given up painting to go back to her hometown

259
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,110
with her family.

260
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:47,690
But I knew

261
00:12:49,020 --> 00:12:50,220
that was impossible.

262
00:12:56,660 --> 00:12:57,920
But in this vast world,

263
00:12:58,420 --> 00:12:59,780
I could only forget her.

264
00:13:03,780 --> 00:13:04,670
Until that day.

265
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,040
Painter Feng.

266
00:13:06,980 --> 00:13:09,510
Are you running errands for Master Wei again?

267
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,710
Please have a look at these paintings.

268
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:18,600
This is so well-painted.

269
00:13:24,830 --> 00:13:27,600
[Spring in Nanfeng Studio, Meng Huaiyun]

270
00:13:35,130 --> 00:13:36,860
I couldn't get it out of my mind.

271
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:37,810
But Master said

272
00:13:38,140 --> 00:13:38,900
Junior had painted that

273
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:39,950
before she left.

274
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:43,710
I wanted to repress myself and forget,

275
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:46,630
until a coincidence occurred.

276
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:48,770
Good wine.

277
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,050
Good wine.

278
00:13:52,050 --> 00:13:53,090
Senior is drunk.

279
00:13:55,380 --> 00:13:55,840
Senior.

280
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:59,080
I'm not drunk.

281
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:00,690
You

282
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:02,360
are definitely drunk.

283
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:06,670
More.

284
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,170
Come on.

285
00:14:09,970 --> 00:14:11,060
The three of us

286
00:14:11,210 --> 00:14:13,260
haven't had so much fun in a long time.

287
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:13,720
Come on.

288
00:14:13,950 --> 00:14:14,540
Cheers!

289
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:20,290
Do you remember

290
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,200
that time we drank with Junior

291
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,800
here?

292
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:26,750
What are you talking about?

293
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,060
Junior,

294
00:14:28,090 --> 00:14:28,940
have you forgotten

295
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:29,450
what we had done

296
00:14:29,450 --> 00:14:30,210
