00:26:15,820 --> 00:26:17,680
He didn't want anyone to save him.

598
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:19,820
He just wanted to find

599
00:26:19,820 --> 00:26:21,020
Meng Huaiyun's body.

600
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:21,710
Also,

601
00:26:22,270 --> 00:26:23,270
he needed someone

602
00:26:24,900 --> 00:26:25,570
to remember

603
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:28,110
all that had happened between them.

604
00:26:28,130 --> 00:26:29,380
You were the only one

605
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:30,250
among us

606
00:26:31,270 --> 00:26:32,870
who found out about his love.

607
00:26:33,900 --> 00:26:34,390
So,

608
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:35,970
you beat me.

609
00:26:37,750 --> 00:26:40,070
I'm not used to

610
00:26:41,170 --> 00:26:42,560
you talking like this.

611
00:26:43,540 --> 00:26:44,760
Are you addicted to being bullied?

612
00:26:44,760 --> 00:26:45,260
Or...

613
00:26:48,140 --> 00:26:49,670
Then I'll use my privilege.

614
00:26:49,900 --> 00:26:50,340
Can I?

615
00:26:50,780 --> 00:26:51,650
Sure, go ahead.

616
00:26:51,780 --> 00:26:52,710
What do you want?

617
00:26:53,020 --> 00:26:54,280
Can I ask for anything?

618
00:26:54,520 --> 00:26:55,320
Tell me first.

619
00:26:56,630 --> 00:26:58,210
I want you to transform

620
00:26:58,620 --> 00:27:00,010
into a puppy

621
00:27:00,150 --> 00:27:01,420
and walk with me around the city.

622
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:02,080
Will you...

623
00:27:03,510 --> 00:27:04,360
Han Zheng.

624
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:06,190
I was just kidding.

625
00:27:06,610 --> 00:27:07,970
Why are you so serious?

626
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:10,810
I only have one request.

627
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:13,260
I have something to tell you,

628
00:27:13,420 --> 00:27:14,980
but you're not allowed to get angry.

629
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:15,310
What?

630
00:27:22,780 --> 00:27:24,370
Does the man with three scars

631
00:27:24,370 --> 00:27:25,570
look like this?

632
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:27,410
Where did you get

633
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:30,200
this portrait?

634
00:27:31,830 --> 00:27:32,710
I found it

635
00:27:32,740 --> 00:27:34,300
in one of the Chief Inspector's

636
00:27:34,300 --> 00:27:35,050
case files.

637
00:27:36,460 --> 00:27:38,390
Why would he investigate this too?

638
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:39,840
I want to know too.

639
00:27:40,980 --> 00:27:41,660
Because

640
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:45,330
the Inspection Bureau's Chief Inspector

641
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:46,780
was my father.

642
00:27:49,150 --> 00:27:51,410
My father went to Shuobei before he died.

643
00:27:52,430 --> 00:27:53,580
After he came back,

644
00:27:54,010 --> 00:27:56,210
he contracted a strange disease

645
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:58,370
and grew black spots all over his body.

646
00:27:59,610 --> 00:28:00,530
Soon after,

647
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:02,430
he died.

648
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:04,640
My mother

649
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,080
raised me, a sickly child,

650
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:06,940
all by herself.

651
00:28:07,780 --> 00:28:09,640
She doesn't want me to take risks.

652
00:28:10,080 --> 00:28:11,740
She just wants me to live well.

653
00:28:13,780 --> 00:28:14,550
Every time

654
00:28:14,580 --> 00:28:15,540
I work with you,

655
00:28:16,020 --> 00:28:18,500
it is like there's a sword hanging over my head.

656
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:19,250
I don't know

657
00:28:20,090 --> 00:28:21,380
if I should take risks

658
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:22,580
to do what I want to do,

659
00:28:23,220 --> 00:28:25,080
or if I should listen to my parents

660
00:28:25,630 --> 00:28:26,700
and live well.

661
00:28:33,090 --> 00:28:33,980
You silly girl.

662
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:37,380
Why do you keep calling me silly?

663
00:28:37,380 --> 00:28:38,980
I'm a reasonable person.

664
00:28:39,870 --> 00:28:40,590
How could I let

665
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:41,240
a little girl

666
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,370
risk her life for me?

667
00:28:43,100 --> 00:28:44,520
But from now on,

668
00:28:45,410 --> 00:28:46,690
you can just order me around.

669
00:28:46,690 --> 00:28:47,620
We are partners.

670
00:28:48,130 --> 00:28:48,580
You

671
00:28:49,020 --> 00:28:50,500
use your brain to the fullest.

672
00:28:50,500 --> 00:28:51,360
As for the rest,

673
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:52,650
just count on me.

674
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:55,590
I just want to know

675
00:28:56,730 --> 00:28:58,020
if the person on this portrait

676
00:28:58,020 --> 00:28:58,790
is really

677
00:28:58,820 --> 00:29:00,120
the man with three scars?

678
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:00,560
Is he?

679
00:29:02,100 --> 00:29:03,580
I...

680
00:29:04,390 --> 00:29:05,070
Look.

681
00:29:05,580 --> 00:29:06,340
You don't want to

682
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:07,450
tell me anything.

683
00:29:07,940 --> 00:29:09,300
Yet you say I'm your good friend

684
00:29:09,300 --> 00:29:10,500
and trusted partner.

685
00:29:10,780 --> 00:29:11,840
You only think of me

686
00:29:11,840 --> 00:29:13,170
as a tool to solve cases.

687
00:29:13,370 --> 00:29:13,730
No.

688
00:29:14,430 --> 00:29:15,900
You're turning it on me.

689
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:21,620
I can only tell you

690
00:29:22,370 --> 00:29:22,970
this man

691
00:29:23,330 --> 00:29:24,260
is called Mu Yan.

692
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:25,250
He is related

693
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:27,030
to the Qi race's secret.

694
00:29:27,350 --> 00:29:28,750
That's all I can tell you.

695
00:29:29,810 --> 00:29:30,840
If I continue,

696
00:29:31,580 --> 00:29:32,690
Chilan might come

697
00:29:32,820 --> 00:29:33,830
to take your life.

698
00:29:35,580 --> 00:29:36,180
By the way,

699
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,630
the disease you just mentioned

700
00:29:39,900 --> 00:29:41,230
is similar to

701
00:29:41,450 --> 00:29:43,660
a type of Xuanqi poison I've seen before.

702
00:29:43,660 --> 00:29:44,120
Poison?

703
00:29:45,170 --> 00:29:45,900
What poison?

704
00:29:46,870 --> 00:29:49,000
The Xuanqi tribe is adept at medicine.

705
00:29:49,730 --> 00:29:50,930
They have always been opposed to

706
00:29:50,930 --> 00:29:52,980
friendly relations between the Qian and Qi.

707
00:29:52,980 --> 00:29:53,610
So it's not surprising

708
00:29:53,610 --> 00:29:55,210
that they would do something

709
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,440
to harm a Qian.

710
00:29:57,690 --> 00:29:58,230
However,

711
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:00,850
what exactly happened to your father?

712
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:03,100
What if the person he met

713
00:30:03,620 --> 00:30:04,420
wasn't Mu Yan?

714
00:30:06,740 --> 00:30:07,850
Is he the one

715
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:09,460
in this portrait?

716
00:30:11,300 --> 00:30:12,640
This portrait looks like the one

717
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:14,340
on the arrest warrant

718
00:30:14,700 --> 00:30:16,560
the state of Qi once issued.

719
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:18,800
Logically speaking,

720
00:30:18,940 --> 00:30:20,070
it shouldn't appear

721
00:30:20,090 --> 00:30:21,020
in Jiuxiao City,

722
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:22,710
nor should it

723
00:30:22,710 --> 00:30:24,770
come into your father's possession.

724
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:27,920
Thank you for trusting me

725
00:30:28,870 --> 00:30:30,130
and telling me so much.

726
00:30:32,190 --> 00:30:33,390
I have to tell you that

727
00:30:34,260 --> 00:30:35,220
if one day,

728
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:36,980
I find out it was Mu Yan

729
00:30:36,980 --> 00:30:38,310
who poisoned my father,

730
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:40,650
I won't let him off the hook.

731
00:30:46,580 --> 00:30:46,940
Here.

732
00:30:47,570 --> 00:30:48,570
Give me your hand.

733
00:30:50,340 --> 00:30:51,400
What are you doing?

734
00:30:53,780 --> 00:30:54,690
This is how the Qi

735
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:55,410
make a vow.

736
00:30:56,110 --> 00:30:56,620
I swear

737
00:30:58,380 --> 00:30:59,220
I will help you

738
00:30:59,720 --> 00:31:01,900
find out the truth of your father's death

739
00:31:01,900 --> 00:31:03,830
and give you a proper explanation.

740
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:06,230
Even if that person were Mu Yan,

741
00:31:07,790 --> 00:31:08,470
I believe

742
00:31:09,390 --> 00:31:10,350
he wouldn't kill a Qian

743
00:31:10,350 --> 00:31:11,150
for no reason.

744
00:31:17,820 --> 00:31:18,300
What?

745
00:31:18,610 --> 00:31:20,140
You still don't believe me?

746
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:23,260
I...

747
00:31:26,210 --> 00:31:27,810
Since Your Highness says so,

748
00:31:27,900 --> 00:31:29,500
of course I believe you.

749
00:31:32,210 --> 00:31:33,800
Can you

750
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:35,780
not call me "Your Highness"?

751
00:31:36,370 --> 00:31:36,970
You can...

752
00:31:37,330 --> 00:31:40,010
just call me Han Zheng.

753
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,990
Why are you suddenly

754
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,020
so amiable?

755
00:31:57,060 --> 00:31:59,210
Did you wrong me

756
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,170
somehow?

757
00:32:02,270 --> 00:32:03,020
Look at you.

758
00:32:03,430 --> 00:32:04,900
Are you picking a fight again?

759
00:32:04,900 --> 00:32:05,900
Do I have to be mean

760
00:32:06,090 --> 00:32:07,020
to calm you down?

761
00:32:15,380 --> 00:32:15,910
Let's go.

762
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:21,780
Actually,

763
00:32:22,290 --> 00:32:23,780
I have been wanting to tell you something.

764
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:25,090
I recognise

765
00:32:25,690 --> 00:32:27,020
you, Su Jiu'er, now.

766
00:32:27,770 --> 00:32:29,110
You are different from

767
00:32:29,660 --> 00:32:30,820
all the other Qian people.

768
00:32:30,820 --> 00:32:32,750
You are qualified to be my partner.

769
00:32:34,170 --> 00:32:34,790
However,

770
00:32:35,100 --> 00:32:35,900
in the future,

771
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,820
I won't say any of these nonsense again.

772
00:32:37,820 --> 00:32:38,960
I won't use them

773
00:32:39,030 --> 00:32:40,290
to control you either.

774
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,000
But can you

775
00:32:41,980 --> 00:32:43,210
not be so silly

776
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:45,470
and risk your life for me again?

777
00:32:52,810 --> 00:32:53,800
Unfortunately,

778
00:32:54,930 --> 00:32:56,460
it's all Yue Daren's fault.

779
00:32:56,940 --> 00:32:58,140
If it weren't for him,

780
00:32:58,540 --> 00:32:59,590
we might have caught that man

781
00:32:59,590 --> 00:33:00,740
that night.

782
00:33:01,580 --> 00:33:02,230
Tell me.

783
00:33:02,820 --> 00:33:03,680
Was that person

784
00:33:03,690 --> 00:33:04,710
the real Mu Yan,

785
00:33:05,010 --> 00:33:06,500
or someone posing as him

786
00:33:06,670 --> 00:33:07,430
to trick you?

787
00:33:08,660 --> 00:33:09,850
We'll find out.

788
00:33:14,630 --> 00:33:14,960
Here.

789
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:16,480
Eat more of this.

790
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:18,040
Become a sweeter talker.

791
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,840
Don't keep arguing with me

792
00:33:19,840 --> 00:33:21,140
out of nowhere.

793
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:24,160
We are opposites.

794
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:26,020
I like to banter with you

795
00:33:26,060 --> 00:33:27,320
when I'm in a good mood.

796
00:33:27,490 --> 00:33:28,300
When I see you get so angry

797
00:33:28,300 --> 00:33:29,500
that you have wrinkles on your face,

798
00:33:29,500 --> 00:33:30,100
I'm happy.

799
00:33:30,820 --> 00:33:32,360
Who has wrinkles on their face?

800
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:32,770
You.

801
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:34,480
-You’re full... -You.

802
00:33:34,480 --> 00:33:35,790
You have wrinkles all over your face.

803
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:37,050
I don't have wrinkles.

804
00:33:38,370 --> 00:33:40,030
I really don't have wrinkles.

805
00:33:48,130 --> 00:33:49,300
Mother, I'm back.

806
00:33:54,260 --> 00:33:54,720
Mother.

807
00:33:55,000 --> 00:33:56,260
Do you want some candy?

808
00:33:59,340 --> 00:34:01,650
You went to see His Highness secretly again?

809
00:34:01,650 --> 00:34:02,650
Not His Highness.

810
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:03,710
It was Han Zheng.

811
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:10,239
He treats you so well.

812
00:34:11,260 --> 00:34:13,120
Daughter, you must lock him down.

813
00:34:14,030 --> 00:34:16,030
Mother, what are you talking about?

814
00:34:16,389 --> 00:34:18,239
We are good partners.

815
00:34:18,940 --> 00:34:20,600
We don't see gender.

816
00:34:23,989 --> 00:34:24,679
Try one.

817
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,800
It's really sweet.

818
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:28,460
Take this red one, it's sweet.

819
00:34:30,170 --> 00:34:30,830
Is it sweet?

820
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:31,900
Very.

821
00:34:39,820 --> 00:34:41,060
The effects of her Qi Vitality Stone

822
00:34:41,060 --> 00:34:42,060
haven't worn off.

823
00:34:42,610 --> 00:34:43,110
I wonder

824
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,219
whose Qi Vitality Stone she used.

825
00:34:45,219 --> 00:34:46,620
Will she dream of that Qi?

826
00:34:47,530 --> 00:34:49,600
If she dreams of another Qi,

827
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:50,940
then...

828
00:34:53,699 --> 00:34:55,230
She won't touch him, right?

829
00:34:57,570 --> 00:34:58,500
Touch his face?

830
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:01,180
No way!

831
00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:05,230
Pinch him like this?

832
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:05,980
No way!

833
00:35:07,330 --> 00:35:08,130
Hold his hand?

834
00:35:09,780 --> 00:35:10,980
She can only touch me—

835
00:35:52,140 --> 00:35:52,940
Painter Feng?

836
00:35:53,930 --> 00:35:54,730
Inspector Su.

837
00:35:55,170 --> 00:35:56,430
Where is your partner?

838
00:35:57,060 --> 00:35:57,800
Did he leave you

839
00:35:57,800 --> 00:35:58,460
alone here?

840
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:01,060
Of course not.

841
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:02,490
How could he?

842
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:04,640
Yes.

843
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:06,870
How could he?

844
00:36:08,180 --> 00:36:09,500
He won't leave you

845
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:10,290
alone here.

846
00:36:13,430 --> 00:36:15,100
So that was what he meant

847
00:36:15,770 --> 00:36:17,130
when he said that

848
00:36:17,970 --> 00:36:18,930
back then.

849
00:36:45,450 --> 00:36:46,310
What happened?

850
00:36:47,130 --> 00:36:49,070
Am I dreaming about this

851
00:36:49,180 --> 00:36:51,180
because I've been thinking about it in the day?

852
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:51,740
Junior.

853
00:36:52,370 --> 00:36:53,350
Stop painting.

854
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:55,390
Tell her now.

855
00:36:57,600 --> 00:36:58,000
You...

856
00:36:59,690 --> 00:37:00,730
You fool.

857
00:37:01,340 --> 00:37:02,380
Why didn't you tell her

858
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:03,500
you liked her

859
00:37:03,740 --> 00:37:05,270
while she was still around?

860
00:37:05,730 --> 00:37:07,160
She likes you too.

861
00:37:09,010 --> 00:37:09,690
Why are you

862
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:10,960
so dull?

863
00:37:11,210 --> 00:37:12,270
He doesn't want to say it.

864
00:37:12,270 --> 00:37:13,270
Why force him?

865
00:37:14,180 --> 00:37:14,820
Han Zheng?

866
00:37:16,020 --> 00:37:17,020
Why are you here?

867
00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:18,360
A dream?

868
00:37:19,040 --> 00:37:20,460
Did she use

869
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:21,660
my Qi Vitality Stone?

870
00:37:30,880 --> 00:37:32,080
That was the time.

871
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:33,440
Fine.

872
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:35,640
You're not an outsider anyway.

873
00:37:36,390 --> 00:37:37,650
This is a dream anyway.

874
00:37:38,100 --> 00:37:39,250
Don't just stand here.

875
00:37:39,250 --> 00:37:40,230
Help them.

876
00:37:40,470 --> 00:37:41,670
Let them be together.

877
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:42,540
Why do you want them

878
00:37:42,540 --> 00:37:43,400
to be together?

879
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:44,340
Why?

880
00:37:45,780 --> 00:37:47,380
Look at how pitiful they are.

881
00:37:47,530 --> 00:37:48,780
Shouldn't people who have feelings for each other

882
00:37:48,780 --> 00:37:49,960
get to be together?

883
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:51,850
Why are you acting so dull too?

884
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:54,840
Weird.

885
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:56,930
Why aren't you talking back

886
00:37:56,930 --> 00:37:58,730
no matter what I say to you today?

887
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:01,140
Smile.

888
00:38:02,130 --> 00:38:02,860
Don't smile.

889
00:38:03,260 --> 00:38:03,990
Smile again.

890
00:38:11,540 --> 00:38:12,740
Are you really a fake?

891
00:38:13,830 --> 00:38:15,200
Since you're a fake,

892
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,660
let me practice on you.

893
00:38:17,230 --> 00:38:18,070
Maybe

894
00:38:18,100 --> 00:38:19,330
when I lie to you in the future,

